title: Fresh Freaks
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Western, Salad bar, Czech, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Fully gluten-free bistro close to park Luzanky. Offers soups, filled wraps, burgers, salads, dessert, and a daily menu. For the veggie burger and veggie items ask to omit cheese for vegan. Irish cider Magners and British Fullers on tap.
